# Refactor ATS Resume Analyzer → Full-Stack SaaS Application

Refactor the existing Streamlit ATS Resume Analyzer into a production-ready full-stack application with a FastAPI backend and Next.js frontend, preserving all business logic (TF-IDF + Cosine Similarity scoring, PDF parsing, NLTK text processing).

## Proposed Changes

### Backend (FastAPI)

#### [NEW] `backend/main.py`
- FastAPI app with CORS middleware (configurable origins via env var)
- `POST /api/analyze` — accepts multipart file upload (PDF/DOCX) + `job_description` form field → returns JSON `{ score, label, feedback }`
- `GET /api/health` — health check endpoint

#### [NEW] `backend/services/pdf_parser.py`
- Port [extract_text_from_pdf()](file:///c:/Users/chira/OneDrive/Desktop/AI-Resume-Reviewer-ATS-Analyzer-main/utils/pdf_parser.py#5-16) from existing code (PyPDF2), remove Streamlit dependency
- Add `extract_text_from_docx()` using `python-docx`

#### [NEW] `backend/services/text_processing.py`
- Port [clean_text()](file:///c:/Users/chira/OneDrive/Desktop/AI-Resume-Reviewer-ATS-Analyzer-main/utils/text_processing.py#14-20), [remove_stopwords()](file:///c:/Users/chira/OneDrive/Desktop/AI-Resume-Reviewer-ATS-Analyzer-main/utils/text_processing.py#22-27), [calculate_similarity()](file:///c:/Users/chira/OneDrive/Desktop/AI-Resume-Reviewer-ATS-Analyzer-main/utils/text_processing.py#29-41) as-is
- NLTK downloads at startup

#### [NEW] `backend/services/analyzer.py`
- `analyze_resume(file_bytes, filename, job_description)` — orchestrates parsing + scoring
- Returns structured result dict with score, label, color, and feedback text

#### [NEW] `backend/requirements.txt`
- `fastapi`, `uvicorn`, `python-multipart`, `PyPDF2`, `python-docx`, `scikit-learn`, `nltk`

#### [NEW] `backend/.env.example`
- `CORS_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000`

---

### Frontend (Next.js + TypeScript + Tailwind CSS)

#### [NEW] `frontend/` — Next.js project scaffolded via `create-next-app`
- TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, App Router

#### Key components:
| Component | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `app/page.tsx` | Main page — hero, upload form, results |
| `components/Hero.tsx` | Animated gradient hero banner |
| `components/FileUpload.tsx` | Drag-and-drop PDF/DOCX upload with validation |
| `components/JobDescription.tsx` | Textarea with character count |
| `components/ResultsCard.tsx` | Animated score display, gauge bar, feedback |
| `components/Navbar.tsx` | Top navigation bar with logo |
| `components/Footer.tsx` | Footer with credits |
| `components/Toast.tsx` | Toast notification system |
| `lib/api.ts` | API client for backend communication |

#### Design system:
- Dark theme by default (slate/zinc palette with purple/cyan accents matching existing brand colors `#6C63FF` / `#48C6EF`)
- Inter font from Google Fonts
- Glassmorphism cards, gradient accents, micro-animations
- Fully responsive (mobile-first)

